# Ignore IDE settings, except the project-level Prettier/ESLint config that
# every contributor needs. Must be `.idea/*` rather than a bare `.idea`:
# excluding the directory itself stops git descending into it, so the negations
# below could not re-include anything. Subdirectories need their own negation
# before a file inside them can.
.idea/*
!.idea/prettier.xml
!.idea/jsLinters/
playground
src/prisma/generated
